  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hitmen Havoc: A Wild Mix of Strategy and Chaos</h2><br><strong>Hitmen Havoc is a cartoony, fast-paced 2D arena party shooter where strategy meets mayhem. Whether you’re battling friends, foes, strangers, or viewers, every match is a fresh and exciting challenge.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose from 8 unique characters, each with their own special skills and stats</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/f20dc063b7004de13ec8c0ee5d47d7d9.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/f20dc063b7004de13ec8c0ee5d47d7d9.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/f20dc063b7004de13ec8c0ee5d47d7d9.mp4?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dive into customizable game modes that keep the action unpredictable and exhilarating. <br>Perfect for quick sessions or lively parties, Hitmen Havoc ensures unforgettable competitive fun with every round.<br><br>Diverse Weapon Arsenal: Arm yourself with a wide array of weapons, each adding a distinct flavor to the chaotic gameplay. From precision shots to explosive mayhem, there's a weapon for every scenario.<br>Dynamic Arenas: Battle across multiple levels, each offering a unique environment and challenges that keep you on your toes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/91f38b4296d0758583ceb9921c1f47ac.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/91f38b4296d0758583ceb9921c1f47ac.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/91f38b4296d0758583ceb9921c1f47ac.mp4?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapon Showcase</h2><br><table><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/e115868fde153f9e3d7c8c85a0663c26.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/e115868fde153f9e3d7c8c85a0663c26.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>Pistol:</strong> Your trusty sidekick! Always there, but don't expect miracles.</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/c311b28fdefa0537160b8780aa797fc3.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/c311b28fdefa0537160b8780aa797fc3.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>SMG:</strong> Spray and pray! Unload a torrent of bullets and watch chaos ensue.</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/8d210704f2e6524dd7d7bce0defa676c.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/8d210704f2e6524dd7d7bce0defa676c.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>Assault Rifle:</strong> Jack of all trades! Steady shots for every vendetta.</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/2e4a08afd93da0b0a273a29ecfba5ab2.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/2e4a08afd93da0b0a273a29ecfba5ab2.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>Laser Blaster:</strong> Zap zap kaboom! Charge it up for a blast that'll leave 'em reeling!</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/058951951dcbab800ad6ff7a039c013c.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/058951951dcbab800ad6ff7a039c013c.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>Crossbow:</strong> Double the trouble! Knock back and hurt, a double whammy!</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/4d159fec92cf1a05afdbf6cfbc95bea1.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/4d159fec92cf1a05afdbf6cfbc95bea1.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>Sniper:</strong> Line 'em up! Penetrate multiple enemies with one devastating shot.</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/aaffc23187c3848cdf238f92ba16aa3a.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/aaffc23187c3848cdf238f92ba16aa3a.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>Punch:</strong> Fist of Fury! Send enemies flying into the afterlife with one punch.</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/1c2df0a730db9090728a633ed127224b.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/1c2df0a730db9090728a633ed127224b.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>Energy Grenades:</strong> Long throw, mighty blow! Charge up to hurl them farther for explosive fun.</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/a0333dce61246cc5473b793593f6762a.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/a0333dce61246cc5473b793593f6762a.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>RPG:</strong> Colossal chaos! Big hits but watch your ammo.</td></tr></table><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Player Testimonials</h2><br><blockquote> \"Had a blast playing Hitmen Havoc with friends online. We couldn't stop laughing at some of the crazy moments during our matches.\" </blockquote><br><blockquote> \"I’m not usually into multiplayer games, but this one hooked me. It’s just plain fun, especially when you’re playing with friends.\" </blockquote><br><blockquote> \"The matches are quick, but they always leave you wanting to play just one more. It’s a great game to unwind with after a long day.\" </blockquote><br><blockquote> \"This game became an instant favorite in our group. We’ve had some epic battles and a lot of laughs.\" </blockquote><br><blockquote> \"Totally addictive. We kept saying 'just one more round,' and before we knew it, hours had passed.\" </blockquote>",
